der border-navy-100","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-navy-700 text-body","children":"Coaching, at its best, sits at a meeting point. From the behavioural sciences, psychology and neuroscience, we inherit a clear understanding of how people actually change. From the world's contemplative and reflective traditions, we inherit something quieter and just as vital: the practice of self-mastery, and the conviction that no one can guide another further than they have travelled themselves."}]}]]}],["$","$L15","1",{"delay":0.1,"className":"relative flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-12 items-start","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"hidden md:flex flex-col items-center mt-2 relative z-10 shrink-0 w-16","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-brand-gold-400 border-[4px] border-cream-50 shadow-sm"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-white p-8 md:p-10 relative rounded-3xl shadow-xl border border-navy-100","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-navy-700 text-body","children":"We also inherit a way of teaching. Craft has always been passed from one person to another, closely and personally, and that is why we train one-to-one rather than in crowded rooms. It is the oldest method there is, and still the best."}]}]]}],["$","$L15","2",{"delay":0.2,"className":"relative flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-12 items-start","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"hidden md:flex flex-col items-center mt-2 relative z-10 shrink-0 w-16","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-brand-gold-400 border-[4px] border-cream-50 shadow-sm"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-white p-8 md:p-10 relative rounded-3xl shadow-xl border border-navy-100","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-navy-700 text-body","children":"So when we speak of heritage, we mean a lineage of ideas about human growth that long predates us, and which we are proud to carry forward with rigour and care."}]}]]}],"$L16"],"$L17"]}]]}]}]}]]}]
